‚úÖ Rule for Value = 1 (F>0%, G>0%)

1. Select: ‚ÄúFormat only cells that contain‚Äù


2. Rule:

Cell Value ‚Üí equal to ‚Üí 1



3. Click Format ‚Üí choose Green fill (or any color)


4. Click OK




