‚úÖ Rule for Value = 2 (F=0%, G>0%)

1. New Rule ‚Üí ‚ÄúFormat only cells that contain‚Äù


2. Cell Value ‚Üí equal to ‚Üí 2


3. Format ‚Üí choose Blue fill


4. OK




